text: Back on the market after strong activity and multiple offers over asking! Inside, the kitchen and bathrooms are tastefully updated, so the heavy lifting is done. A finished basement adds bonus living space for a rec room, home gym, or office, plus extra storage. Big-ticket item handled: roof replaced ~8 years ago. Easy indooroutdoor flow, move-in ready condition, and plenty of room to spread outcome see it!

Just off the kitchen, a spacious laundry/mudroom provides convenience with access to the full updated bath and two additional bedrooms, while a third bedroom is located off the living room. Outside, enjoy a private backyard with mature trees, a detached garage, and room to relax or entertain. Welcome Home!

text: Check out this incredible all brick and vinyl ranch with attached 2 car garage nestled on a beautiful street in Warren, north of I-696. This home has gorgeous curb appeal with tasteful, mature landscaping surrounding it, and a stamped concrete approach and porch. The attached garage (with garage door opener) offers plenty of space for a car, as well as storage, and easy access into your home on those cold and wet days. Some of the extras include Anderson vinyl windows throughout the home, a brand new water tank, high end ceiling fans in the kitchen and family room, recessed lighting in the kitchen, some upgraded light fixtures and a natural fireplace in the family room, with sliding doors leading to a patio. The front door has also been upgraded and features beveled glass. The living room is spacious, with decorative ceiling molding, and a large picture window, allowing in plenty of natural light. The hallway leads to three nicely sized bedrooms with plenty of closet space and a large full bathroom with custom tile and plenty of storage. Next to the living room is a large open concept kitchen and dining area with tile backsplashes, recessed lighting and plenty of workspace. This room also offers natural light from the windows in the dining area, and a ton of storage space with deep cupboards and a built-in pantry. The stainless appliances remain with the home. Through the doorway is the huge family room. This area is perfect for entertaining or relaxing with its abundant space, beautifully bricked natural fireplace and huge sliding doors that lead to the cement patio and large, back yard. In the corner of the yard is a shed, perfect for lawn equipment, furniture or toys. The full basement is partially finished and has a half bath and a bar against one wall. This area is ready for your incredible ideas, either creating another living space or weight room or home office area. Also included in the full basement is the laundry room. The appliances remain with the home. This gorgeous, all brick and vinyl ranch off

Brick ranch with nice updates in quiet north Warren neighborhood. Custom designed and professionally installed rock/perennial gardens with 40 year weed barrier. The covered front porch is private and perfectly framed in hydrangeas - a wonderful spot to relax and watch the world go by. Inside, the formal living room is spacious and bright, with hardwood floors, large picture window and plaster walls. The kitchen was renovated in 2021 with white shaker cabinets, granite counters, stone backsplash and upgraded stainless appliances. The family room has wood floors, fireplace with a brick hearth with electric insert, and direct access to your own private backyard oasis. Half bath on the first floor plus bonus room that could be first floor laundry, study, or walk-in pantry. Three spacious bedrooms all with hardwood floors and ceiling fans. The main bathroom has double sinks, ceramic tile and updated fixtures. Huge basement is awaiting your finishing touches. 2 car attached garage. The whole house is fresh and clean with unique trim and touches throughout.

Peace of mind comes easy with a long list of updates: roof and gutters (2023), furnace (December 2015), A/C (2016), hot water tank (approx. 2021), windows (approx. 2 years), and an updated front entry door with beautiful leaded glass. This home combines charm, functionality, and modern updatesall ready for its next owner!

text: Go Big AND Go Home! This large 4 bedroom 2.1 Bath Raised Ranch is the one you've been waiting for! Almost 3, 000 sf of total living space is waiting for you. Lovingly owned for almost 50 years, this seller has pride of ownership throughout. Take notice of the gleaming hardwood floors in the step down living room with a bay window. A perfect place to admire your beautiful landscaping in the front yard. The primary suite has 2 large closets while the 2nd bedroom is being used as an office. They share the meticulously maintained main bath that is ultra groovy! The kitchen was remodeled with an added peninsula for easy entertaining and everyday living, beautiful granite tops, stainless appliances and tons of countertop space and storage. The nook area opens to the family room where new Pella windows were installed in 2023 and Pella doorwall(2007) overlooks the large fenced in yard. The brick paver patio sets the stage to relax and unwind while being able to picture family gatherings and endless laughs while enjoying this great space! The attached 2 car garage with garage door(installed in 2008) is an extra bonus. Head downstairs to the finished lower level with a bar, workout area, game room and laundry room. The 2nd floor addition was completed in 1997 with 2 more spacious bedrooms and closets with custom shelving. All new Pella windows installed there in 2023. A large full bath completes this space. New Roof in 2016 as well as gutter guards both with a Lifetime transferable warranty. Enjoy Peace of mind with nothing else to do but move right in! Welcome Home!

Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath brick ranch, featuring a spacious 2.5-car garage and numerous updates for peace of mind. Enjoy relaxing mornings in the bright sun porch or entertaining in the fully fenced backyardperfect for kids, pets, and gatherings. Recent updates include a new furnace, hot water tank, updated electrical, front door and a new garage door, ensuring comfort and efficiency. The partially finished basement boasts a natural fireplace, creating a cozy space for those cool evenings. All appliances stay, making this home truly move-in ready! Dont miss your chance to own this cute and cozy ranch in a desirable locationClose proximity to restaurants, schools, expressways, shopping and parks. Schedule your showing today!

Step into timeless character with this spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bath Tudor-style colonial offering over 1,400 sq ft of living space. Built in 1946, this home blends vintage charm with thoughtful updates. Inside, you'll find beautifully refinished oak hardwood floors, a formal dining room with elegant cove ceilings, and a cozy library/den accented by knotty pine paneling. The large eat-in kitchen provides plenty of space for gatherings and features updated flooring, while the bathroom has been refreshed with modern ceramic finishes. Fresh interior paint throughout makes this home move-in ready. The basement, filled with daylight windows, adds storage and the potential for future living space. Set on nearly half an acre, the property boasts an oversized yard ideal for entertaining, gardening, or simply relaxing outdoors. A unique opportunity to own a home with character, space, and charm.. right here in Warren!

Here is a great multifamily property for a savvy investor for a huge, brick triplex north of 9 Mile in Warren! Within the property, there are two, 1BR units and one, 2BR unit. Currently, two of the units are rented below market value at $750 (2BR) and $580 (1BR). The property was most recently rental certified in April 2025, and there is still some meat on the bones to make cosmetic improvements and increase both rents and property value. There are separate gas and electric meters for each unit, and the owner pays the water bill. Overall, awesome opportunity to pick up three units set up for monster cash flow.

Newer interior doors, lights, exterior doors (Andersen), gutters, oak shelving in closets, Ceramic tile in bath, wood blinds, windows, paint and so much more. Copper plumbing and whole house fan round it out. All appliances are negotiable.

text: Welcome to this well-maintained 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home in Warren offering a full basement, and a spacious two-car garage. Owned and lovingly cared for by the same family for 45 years, this home is filled with warmth and pride of ownership. In recent years, the sellers have invested in the big-ticket items that matter most. A new roof, windows, and driveway were all completed in 2017, along with other essential improvements throughout the home. Even better, a brand new air conditioning unit was installed in July 2025, giving buyers peace of mind and year-round comfort. Inside, youll find a cozy floor plan with plenty of natural light, comfortable living spaces, and three inviting bedrooms. The partially finished basement (with fireplace) offers valuable storage and potential for additional living space, while the fenced backyard and garage add both function and convenience. Perfectly located near shopping, dining, and major expressways, this home is ideal for first-time buyers, downsizers, or anyone looking for a move-in ready property where the costly updates have already been taken care of. Dont miss your chance to own this beautifully cared-for homeschedule your showing today!

text: Completely remodeled 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home located in Warren! This charming home features a welcoming living space with freshly painted walls all throughout, new luxury laminate flooring in the kitchen & bathroom, and freshly stained natural hardwood floors throughout the remainder of the home. The open space kitchen includes newer stainless steel appliances, well-maintained cabinetry, new under-cabinet lighting and a modern faucet, blending function with timeless style. The bathroom boasts a full upgrade with new luxury tile, new toilet, new vanity with sink and faucet, a stylish mirror, new light fixture, and a new shower head. Inside both bedrooms you'll find new light fixtures with ceiling fans, as well as new window blinds that offer privacy and a clean, finished look. The home also contains a 'whole house fan' as well as a window AC unit, so you will stay nice and cool during summer months. One standout feature of this beautiful home is the rare basement - a unique find in this neighborhood. It provides ample space to store all your belongings. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a large 1-car garage. All the work has been donejust move in and enjoy!

Pride of ownership shines throughout this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath ranch located on a spacious corner lot in Warren. Featuring a full brick exterior and thoughtful upgrades, this home offers comfort, style, and functionality. Interior Features: Updated kitchen with granite countertops; renovated main bath with ceramic tile and granite finishes; family room with fireplace; living room with hardwood floors; finished basement with full second kitchen. Cement patio with vinyl railing and ample space for entertaining. Beautifully landscaped corner lot. This home is move-in ready and ideal for easy living. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and major roadways. A must-see for buyers seeking quality, care, and value.

text: Solid Brick Ranch with Great Potential! Step into this well-built 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath ranch offering timeless charm and endless opportunity. Situated on a spacious fenced lot, this home features a solid brick exterior, newer windows, and an updated furnace and hot water tank. Hardwood floors lie beneath the carpet, just waiting to be revealed. Bright and open living room with bay window. Spacious kitchen loaded with storage and cabinet drawers, stainless steel refrigerator, built-in microwave and dishwasher. Enjoy the cozy, retro feel of the older finished basement, complete with a wet bar and pool table-perfect for entertaining. The 2-car garage includes a heated attached workshop, ideal for hobbyists or extra storage. Out back, a covered patio with built-in BBQ this area provides a great space to relax and enjoy the yard. While the home does need cosmetic updates, it has great bones and is ready for your personal touch. Also included is a two year old front-load washer and dryer. A solid opportunity in a desirable neighborhood-don't miss out on making it your own!

The fully finished basement includes a bonus room ideal for an office, gym, or guest space. Additional highlights: thirdcar garage, fully paid-off solar panel system, and exceptional maintenance inside and out. A rare find in one of Warren's most desirable areas!

text: Welcome to your dream home at 8244 Hupp Avenue! This stunning, newly renovated 3-bedroom, 2-full-bath gem is move-in ready and boasts modern upgrades throughout.
